title: M. C. Beaton-Agatha Raisin and the Vicious Vet
description:
Agatha Raisin and the Vicious Vet
by M. C. Beaton

 

Agatha hasn't quite adjusted to the pace of village life, or to the failures of her overtures to her handsome neighbor, James Lacey. Since the new vet in town is young and good looking, Agatha's perfectly healthy tabby endures a nasty physical exam in the name of romance. When the vet is found dead, Agatha convinces James that playing amateur detective might be funÂ—until snooping becomes a motivation for murder
